To welcome the small on the island the mayor Filippo Mannino who promoted the idea of assigning her honorary citizenship, deliberated by the municipal council. Citizenship that was conferred on Saturday afternoon, when in Via Roma the playground created with the Fami Funds of the Interior Ministry was always named to Maria. Mary's parents also expressed their intention to baptize the child on its island. The parish priest, already contacted, gave the way free and already found the white tutina that Mary will wear for the ceremony.&nbsp;
